	<conbody>
		<section id="guideline_term">
			<p>A guideline is a recommendation about how to perform a task or set of tasks.</p>
			<p>Guidelines generally reflect  an organization's policies or "groundrules," or they explain how "best results" (in a technology sense or for consistency of results) can be obtained.</p>
		</section>
